Help on skill: strike
Skill type: offensive
Usage duration: random
Affecting stats: Str/Dex/Weapon

A furious strike with a weapon is a part of the barbarian battle style.
This skill is not supposed to resolve a fight, but increase the 
possibility of victory. One needs a weapon to use this skill.
When used in combat, berserking highly increases the damage done. 

When used on a beat up opponent, there is a chance to score a tremendous
blow. Your weapon skill affects the damage done by this skill.
